Hana El Zahed (amụrụ na 5 Jenụwarị 1994) bụ onye Egypt na-eme ihe nkiri.
O mere ihe nkiri mbụ ya na ihe nkiri Al Meshakhsaty na 2003
N'afọ 2009, ọ pụtara dị ka nwa nwa nke onye na-eme ihe nkiri Mohamed Sobhi na usoro TV Yawmeyat Wanees we Ahfadoh
El Zahed mechara kwụsị ọrụ ime ihe nkiri ya. Ọ kọwara mmalite nke ọrụ nka ya dị ka nke a na-emeghị atụmatụ ya, mana ọ bịara site na ndabara.
El Zahed maliteghachiri ọrụ ime ihe nkiri ya na ihe nkiri Jimmy's Plan nke afọ 2014
Ka e mesịrị n'afọ ahụ, e gosiri ya na usoro TV nke Tamer Hosny Farq Tawqit N'afọ 2015, El Zahed nwere ọrụ na usoro TV Alf Leila wa Leila, Mawlana El-aasheq, na El Boyoot Asrar
N'afọ sochirinụ, ọ pụtara na Al Mizan Na Mee 2017, El Zahed pụtara na usoro TV Fel La La Land, nke Mustafa Saqr dere ma bụrụ nke Ahmed el-Gendy duziri
Usoro ahụ ghọrọ otu n'ime ndị Egypt kacha ele anya na YouTube. O nwekwara ọrụ na egwuregwu Ahlan Ramadan N'afọ 2018, El Zahed pụtara na ihe nkiri Sons of Adam
N'ọnwa Febụwarị 2019, El Zahed gosipụtara dika Gamila na ihe nkiri Love Story

Ọ pụtara na usoro TV El wad sayed el shahat na Mee, n'akụkụ onye ọlụlụ ya Ahmed Fahmy. El Zahed lụrụ Fahmy na 11 Septemba 2019 n'ememe dị egwu, na Mohamed Hamaki na-agụ egwu ya. N'oge ezumike ezumike ya, a kpọgara ya n'ụlọ ọgwụ na-arịa nje afọ na Singapore. N'afọ 2020, El Zahed pụtara na ihe nkiri na-atọ ọchị The Washing Machine n'akụkụ Mahmoud Hemida
Ọ bụ Essam Abdel Hamid duziri ya ma mee n'ọdịnihu. A katọrọ ihe nkiri ahụ maka ime n'etiti ọrịa COVID-19. N'ọnwa Julaị 2020, ndị ikom nọ n'ụgbọala wakporo ya mgbe ọ na-akwọ ụgbọala n'èzí Cairo.
